cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with video segmentation and boundary detection. It may also belong to Multimedia (cs.MM) as it deals with video analysis. Additionally, it may belong to Machine Learning (cs.LG) as it proposes a method based on point-wise mutual information. Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) is also a possibility as the proposed method involves reasoning about region assignments. Finally, it may belong to Graphics (cs.GR) as it deals with spatio-temporal voxels.
